title: Summer Blue By Keep It 100 (OG Summer Blue)
description: OG Summer Blue formerly known as Blue Slushie Lemonade is a super tasty vape blend of berry-infused lemonade that will remind you of your favorite blue slushie drink with tart and tangy citrus notes. This refreshing mixed berry and lemonade juice will definitely become your new all day vape! You really can't go wrong with any flavors from Keep it 100 line up. They are among our top selling e liquids.
